{"tid":2264003,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"本港第3季末，負資產住宅按揭貸款宗數199宗，按季增加72宗，增幅近57%","createTime":"2020-10-30T09:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T12:18:30.000Z","uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0b78847e214fb31a0884363d6850707ac4db6bd5","tid":2264003,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:48:11.000Z","msg":"金管局數據顯示，本港第3季末，負資產住宅按揭貸款宗數199宗，按季增加72宗，增幅近57%。<br />\n<br />\n金管局指，這些個案涉及銀行職員的住屋按揭貸款或按揭保險計劃的貸款，而這類貸款的按揭成數一般較高。<br />\n<br />\n至於負資產住宅按揭貸款涉及的金額，增至11.55億元，按季急升近59%。當中，無抵押部分的金額增至3300萬元，按季升50%。<br />\n<br />\n銀行自2011年首季起，並無錄得任何拖欠3個月以上的負資產住宅按揭貸款紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557520-20201030.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557520-20201030.htm&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdt8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=aecc75d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557520-20201030.htm&h=b3f7823b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557520-20201030.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b7d200d7af72f4a6f2f77e01cfc6bf6c99933992","tid":2264003,"uid":281072,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T09:49:51.000Z","msg":"得果少少，增10000%先再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5232e8f1c7e1b689f2c58c1db6c167f4998d057","tid":2264003,"uid":169071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T11:26:07.000Z","msg":"得個199個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f507096e275c328f2361b7f09aad42c8a2655f","tid":2264003,"uid":92125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T11:27:16.000Z","msg":"又唔係call loan"},{"pid":"41f329147f9d26bc97ee5c89bdc23429d4185807","tid":2264003,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T12:07:17.000Z","msg":"引AA9既topic"},{"pid":"d76d